{"tid":466745,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盲光社：六成青少年無法停止上網","createTime":"2017-11-13T00:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T00:39:42.000Z","uid":136994,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c4c084d7b7af97aa488dc894f2824726de378c2b","tid":466745,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T00:34:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=242931\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D242931&d=ToY5HEM1M9s7pBlllVuXYuPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=8b65e00e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D242931&h=34d2c598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=242931</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】有調查發現，六成青少年無法減少上網主要是因為缺乏親友陪伴。<br />\n<br />\n明光社、香港基督少年軍等去年三月合辦「全城褪網運動」，鼓勵青少年在活動當晚停止上網四小時。及後訪問超過1800位中小學參加者，結果發現約六成人無法褪網，當中大約兩成人完全沒有停止上網。他們平日習慣上網三小時或以上；而未能成功褪網，主要原因是沒有親友陪伴，相反能夠成功褪網的人六成當晚有親友陪伴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n盲光社正戇撚柒鳩<br />\n而家乜撚嘢年代呀？<br />\n上網咪上網關你個盲光社乜柒事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前啲人都唔用電㗎<br />\n不如叫全港人唔用電四個鐘呀笨柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650893e671a71cce7877ea84e8e0e2d07541bb4b","tid":466745,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T00:36:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84fe65ffa53c569ebc1e43f3785ef4cbad075e73","tid":466745,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T00:39:42.000Z","msg":"Full day 開wifi<br />\n3部device<br />\n係咪當上網300%?"}]}